Flashing Convoys eyes show the timer as he looks at Dark "That's all I need"  
as A seal appears on his right hand the one he unlocked in Japan.   As he 
open his right it small turbine sits in his palm as it starts spinning 
creating a long lance of ice as shoots it at Dark. 

Dark in shock "That not on the data file." As slides out the way of the ice 
crystal it hits the ground and shatters sending shards into darks back. 
"ARRRRRGGGGGHHHH"
